{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_07_01_short",
  "title": "小美山愛 1話 前を向き駆け抜けろですよ！ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "ファン！　感！　謝！　祭！　ですよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "F! A! N! Festival! Yay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんだ、急に\nテンションが高くないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-What’s going on?\nYou’re really hyped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6235907674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです！\n最高の気分ですよ！　うふふ、うふふふ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course!\nI’m feeling amazing! Haha‚ hahaha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.2333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "だって、だって……憧れの曲！　『GIRI-GIRI\nborderless world』を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because‚ because… it’s my favorite song! ‘GIRI-GIRI\nborderless world’ that――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6666677475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "四人で歌えることになったんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "we get to sing as a group of four!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.718572267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワのファン感謝祭でやるリメイク曲……\n二人時代の曲を四人で歌う企画だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The remake song for LizNoir’s fan festival…\nThe project to sing a song from the duo days with all four members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9000010808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ファン投票でこの曲に決まったじゃないですか！\n私もすっごくすっごく好きな曲なので、嬉しいんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ the fans voted for this song!\nI love this song so much‚ I’m so happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3666677475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……莉央さんと葵さんのクールなのに熱い歌声に\n練習生時代から、何度励まされてきたことか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Rio-san and Aoi-san’s cool yet passionate voices\nhave encouraged me so many times since I was a trainee…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4000026067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "それを、私達も同じステージで一緒に歌えるなんて\n夢みたいです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To think we’ll be singing it together on the same stage‚\nit feels like a dream…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.4333359401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、私達の衣装も作ってもらえるそうですし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ we’re getting our own outfits made!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.149162992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_07_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "GIRI-GIRIまで全力で\n命の音を燃やしてみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "GIRI-GIRI until the very edge‚\nI’ll burn with the sound of life!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3000013352,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}